== 争议与批评 ==
=== 选举舞弊的指控 ===
俄罗斯选举监督组织表示这次选举普遍存在选举舞弊。独立选举监督组织Golos表示，在从9月17日至19日连续三天的俄罗斯选举中观察到大规模的侵犯观察员、委员会成员和候选人权利的情况<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=As it Happened: Russia Votes|url=https://www.themoscowtimes.com/2021/09/19/as-it-happened-russia-votes-a75070|access-date=2021-09-20|date=2021-09-19|last=Times|first=The Moscow|work=The Moscow Times|language=en|archive-date=2021-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211130224744/https://www.themoscowtimes.com/2021/09/19/as-it-happened-russia-votes-a75070|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=Выборы в России - партия Путина побеждает, Google и Apple против российской оппозиции - JAMnews|url=https://jam-news.net/ru/выборы-в-россии-партия-путина-побежда/|access-date=2021-09-20|date=2021-09-19|work=JAMnews in Russian|language=ru-RU|archive-date=2021-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210921093258/https://jam-news.net/ru/%D0%B2%D1%8B%D0%B1%D0%BE%D1%80%D1%8B-%D0%B2-%D1%80%D0%BE%D1%81%D1%81%D0%B8%D0%B8-%D0%BF%D0%B0%D1%80%D1%82%D0%B8%D1%8F-%D0%BF%D1%83%D1%82%D0%B8%D0%BD%D0%B0-%D0%BF%D0%BE%D0%B1%D0%B5%D0%B6%D0%B4%D0%B0/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。Golos同时也接到许多投票违规行为，包括选票在未密封的容器中过夜或在没有视频监控的房间存放的报告，选举观察员因举报违规行为而受到恐吓、威胁甚至拘留的情况<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":1" />。而社交媒体上也流传着几段显示涉嫌欺诈的视频，包括在投票站以外出现选票，向支持[[統一俄羅斯|统一俄罗斯]]的选民派发现金<ref>{{Cite web|title=Communists, observers report violations in Russian election|url=https://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/communists-observers-report-violations-duma-election-80094316|access-date=2021-09-21|last=News|first=A. B. C.|work=ABC News|language=en|archive-date=2021-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211115203511/https://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/communists-observers-report-violations-duma-election-80094316|dead-url=no}}</ref>、强迫投票<ref>{{Cite web|title=Early results in Russia show pro-Kremlin party leads | Taiwan News | 2021-09-20 06:04:00|url=https://www.taiwannews.com.tw/en/news/4291965|access-date=2021-09-21|last=News|first=Taiwan|work=Taiwan News|archive-date=2021-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210921035329/https://www.taiwannews.com.tw/en/news/4291965|dead-url=no}}</ref>，也有民众投诉在投票期间被阻止进入投票站<ref>{{Cite web|title=Вбросы бюллетеней и нападения на наблюдателей|url=https://www.kavkazr.com/a/vbrosy-byulleteney-i-napadeniya-na-nablyudateley/31467799.html|access-date=2021-09-20|work=RFE/RL|language=ru|archive-date=2021-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210921045547/https://www.kavkazr.com/a/vbrosy-byulleteney-i-napadeniya-na-nablyudateley/31467799.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

尽管在选举中，俄罗斯官员试图限制在投票站使用摄像机，但仍不断传出明显的违规投票内容，例如[[亚博卢|亚博卢]]分享在投票中心的违规视频。亚博卢的投票监督员分享来自[[薩馬拉|萨马拉]]一个投票站的一段视频显示，该投票站上午几乎空无一人，而该地区的官方投票却在9月18日记录了大约1,600张选票。另有视频显示，一名妇女在投票时试图利用俄罗斯国旗挡住，然后将一叠选票扔进投票箱 <ref name=":1" /><ref name=":0" />。俄罗斯中央选举委员会也展示在9月18至19日[[斯塔夫罗波尔边疆区|斯塔夫罗波尔边疆区]][[皮亚季戈尔斯克|皮亚季戈尔斯克]]的一处投票站内的摄像镜头被人用一块抹布盖住<ref name=":2">{{Cite web|title=Григорьев: избирательные комиссии быстро принимают решения по нарушениям на выборах|url=https://www.pnp.ru/social/grigorev-izbiratelnye-komissii-bystro-prinimayut-resheniya-po-narusheniyam-na-vyborakh.html|access-date=2021-09-20|work=www.pnp.ru|language=ru|archive-date=2021-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210921110811/https://www.pnp.ru/social/grigorev-izbiratelnye-komissii-bystro-prinimayut-resheniya-po-narusheniyam-na-vyborakh.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

